.TH "ccw_device_set_options_mask" 9 "ccw_device_set_options_mask" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ccw_device_set_options_mask \- set some options and unset the rest
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" ccw_device_set_options_mask
.BI "(struct ccw_device *cdev "  ","
.BI "unsigned long flags "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cdev" 12
device for which the options are to be set
.IP "flags" 12
options to be set
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
All flags specified in \fIflags\fP are set, all flags not specified in \fIflags\fP
are cleared.
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success, -EINVAL on an invalid flag combination.
